<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.5.1">
<l>antāmat taṉpuceyteṉ ṉāvicē rammāṉuk</l>
<l>kantāma vāḻmuṭicaṅ kāḻinū lāramuḷa</l>
<l>centā maraittaṭaṅkaṇ ceṅkaṉivāy ceṅkamalañ</l>
<l>centā maraiyaṭikkaḷ cempoṉ ṟiruvaṭampē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To the lord who joined my soul, making love [to me] in a pretty spot</l>
<l>there are a crown in which a pretty garland lives, a conch, a diskus, a thread [and] a necklace,</l>
<l>on [his] red golden luminous body with red lotus feet,</l>
<l>red lotusses, red fruit mouth [and] large red lotus eyes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
